{"tid":1400181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"be water！分享下當年幫秀吉統一天下嘅黑田如水嘅《水五訓》","createTime":"2019-08-03T11:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:09:18.000Z","uid":170285,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"523f011dda0b26638c4155a1b3e5a7c5957890e2","tid":1400181,"uid":170285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"黑田考高 水五訓<br />\n<br />\n一.自己流動，且能推動他物者，是為水。                                                                             <br />\n<br />\n二.遭障礙時，水花激揚而起，氣勢更勝百倍，是為水。<br />\n<br />\n三.川流不息，精益求精，是為水。<br />\n<br />\n四.自清而後清別的污濁，清濁兼容，是為水。<br />\n<br />\n五.因博大而能注滿大海，蒸發後成雲成雨，結凍後便成晶瑩剔透的冰雪，而不失本性，是為水。    <br />\n<br />\n上網搵出來嘅翻譯<br />\n<br />\n套用返係而家香港嘅情況，我嘅理解如下<br />\n<br />\n一. 追求自由民主的理想，並將其推廣至身邊人。<br />\n<br />\n二.一般以禮待人，但遇到鎮壓會群起反抗。<br />\n<br />\n三.尋找不同的方法去推動、延續這運動，迫政府回應。<br />\n<br />\n四.不停反思，並包容他人的意見。<br />\n<br />\n五.各位出身各異，身處社會不同階層，但卻擁有共同理想，在自己崗位貢獻一份力。<br />\n<br />\nBe water 而家大家都識講<br />\n係時候擴充佢嘅含意！<br />\n希望幫到大家"},{"pid":"0efefef4489b792ab68ad84ac4d98c1ae0977c42","tid":1400181,"uid":170285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:43:01.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e48e104ffac5b3964e5e1f4bce01cbbc78523c","tid":1400181,"uid":170285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a08c8315aab2f763a0abae28ed3e485b866596","tid":1400181,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:50:40.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"41c20d90f9be9f5a017d6396a362522a8214fb20","tid":1400181,"uid":170285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 